<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">红色作品线上投票环节来啦</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">请为你心中满意的作品打call吧</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">由于参展作品较多</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">我们将分为两期展示</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">本期为第一期</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">（投票见推文末尾）</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/2n18Qa8gmEL5q8UIPcPPSy9ibgVcthPNCbK1UBHBQQL9QIJjiaHSu2f5ToXSGJmb8pRTTLx7CcgDibqWfloWXzk1A/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1" alt="图片" width="576" height="676" style="width: 576px; height: 676px;"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">本次“红色作品展”完美闭幕</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">在实施过程中取得了显著的成果</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">学生们通过参观</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">厚植了家国情怀</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">培养了世界胸怀</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">在实践中汲取奋进之力量</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">强青春之担当</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">让红色基因散发出时代光芒！</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 24px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">快来为你们喜欢的选手投票吧！</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240418/1713430515588034993.png" title="1713430515588034993.png" alt="image.png" width="499" height="368" style="width: 499px; height: 368px;"/></p><p style="text-align: center;"><br/></p>